  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="3170292">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3170292/" class="title-link">南公</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3170292"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/T.T/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1174448-6.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/T.T/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Sissi tattoo</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-04-15"
      class="main-meta">2010-04-15 17:19:18</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3170292_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  儿时便知道南怀瑾，母亲最爱的书籍之一，一直没有拜读过，今日偶然结缘于光合书店，果然如预想般的好，大智之人便是如此吧，老子起先读过原文，后在西四听过一节课，那时的我认为老子太理想化，不以为然，今次再慢慢读来，似是终于理解了些，庄子未系统看过，不予评论。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
