  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5669014">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5669014/" class="title-link">彻底改变我的一本书</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5669014"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/Taemia/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u64661732-9.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Taemia/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">晓旭SHINee</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-11-25"
      class="main-meta">2012-11-25 22:22:35</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5669014_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  心情很差很烦躁很孤独的时候偶然认识了这本书。猛然发现，老庄是个神秘而美好的世界。真的，这个世界太复杂，人心太复杂，有时候真的感觉到活得很累，不知道人生的目的究竟在何处。然而南怀瑾大师将老庄经典娓娓道来，让我顿悟。心静，才能摒除烦恼，才能乐以忘忧，才能快乐地...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5669014_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5669014_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





